OL,3,CTeenager jailed for murder of 16-year-
OL,4,Cold Harry Pitman on New Year's Eve
OL,6,FBodycam footage shows the moment Lloyd-
OL,7,FHall was arrested.
OL,9,FA teenager has been jailed for at
OL,10,Fleast 16 years for stabbing a 16-year-
OL,11,Fold boy in the neck at a New Year's
OL,12,FEve firework event.
OL,14,FAreece Lloyd-Hall, 18, attacked Harry
OL,15,FPitman after he accidentally bumped
OL,16,Finto another boy while playfighting on
OL,17,FPrimrose Hill, north London, the Old
OL,18,FBailey had heard.
