OL,3,CTeenager jailed for murder of 16-year-
OL,4,Cold Harry Pitman on New Year's Eve
OL,6,FThe incident happened in front of
OL,7,Fpolice officers and crows who had
OL,8,Fgathered in the popular park to watch
OL,9,Ffireworks over the River Thames on
OL,10,FDecember 31 2023.
OL,12,FFollowing two trials, Lloyd-Hall, from
OL,13,FWestminster, was found guilty of
OL,14,Fmurder and having an offensive weapon.
OL,16,FIn a televised sentencing, Mr Justice
OL,17,FCavanagh said Mr Pitman had been a
OL,18,Fnormal "boisterous and exuberant" 16-
OL,19,Fyear-old who was "full of charm".
