OL,6,F"This case is the clearest possible
OL,7,Ftragic illustration of the dangers of
OL,8,Fyoung people carrying knives in public.
OL,10,F"I hope that this case will serve as a
OL,11,Fwarning and as a deterrent to young
OL,12,Fpeople who are thinking of carrying a
OL,13,Fknife, even if they delude themselves
OL,14,Finto thinking it is useful for self-
OL,15,Fdefence."
OL,17,FMembers of Harry's family tearfully
OL,18,Fembraced after Lloyd-Hall was sent
OL,19,Fdown from the dock.
