OL,6,FEarlier, Harry's older sister Tayla
OL,7,FLohan told how the family struggled to
OL,8,Fcome to terms with the "senseless and
OL,9,Fbrutal" way he was killed.
OL,11,FOn hearing that he had been hurt, his
OL,12,Fparents had rushed to the park to be
OL,13,Fwith their son, she told the court.
OL,15,FReading a victim impact statement on
OL,16,Fbehalf of the family, she said: "As a
OL,17,Ffamily we all feel guilty that year,
OL,18,F2023, was the first year we had not
OL,19,Fall celebrated together. Harry went
OL,20,Fout to celebrate with his friends and
OL,21,Fhe did not come home."
