OL,6,FShe described Harry as bright, full of
OL,7,Fenergy and a natural entrepreneur who
OL,8,Fhad studied law at college and aspired
OL,9,Fto follow his great grandfather into a
OL,10,Fcareer in the army.
OL,12,F'You stabbed Harry because you lost
OL,13,Fyour temper with him and you acted
OL,14,Flike a big man in front of your
OL,15,Ffriends'
OL,17,FPreviously, prosecutor Jocelyn Ledward
OL,18,FKC had described how "revelry turned
OL,19,Fto tragedy in the blink of an eye" on
OL,20,FNew Year's Eve 2023.
