OL,6,FHarry and Lloyd-Hall were strangers to
OL,7,Feach other and had gone to watch the
OL,8,Ffireworks with different groups of
OL,9,Ffriends.
OL,11,FEarlier in the evening, special
OL,12,Fconstable David Smith said Harry
OL,13,Fseemed excitable and had "physically
OL,14,Fbounced" up to him to engage in
OL,15,Ffriendly chat.
OL,17,FHe went on to "fist bump" another man
OL,18,Fwho had gone to watch the fireworks
OL,19,Fwith his family.
