OL,6,FThe fatal incident appeared to have
OL,7,Fbeen sparked by a scuffle between
OL,8,FHarry and one of the defendant's
OL,9,Ffriends shortly after 11.30pm.
OL,11,FLloyd-hall had pushed forward and
OL,12,Flunged at Harry with a pointed dagger,
OL,13,Fmetres from where uniformed police
OL,14,Fofficers were stationed.
OL,16,F'This case is the clearest possible
OL,17,Ftragic illustration of the dangers of
OL,18,Fyoung people carrying knives in public'
