OL,3,CTeenager jailed for murder of 16-year-
OL,4,Cold Harry Pitman on New Year's Eve
OL,6,FIn mobile phone footage played in
OL,7,Fcourt, a knife sheath was seen to fly
OL,8,Fthrough the air during the fast-paced
OL,9,Fincident.
OL,11,FHarry held his neck, his white T-shirt
OL,12,Fcovered in blood, as he pushed through
OL,13,Fcrowds calling to officers for help
OL,14,Fhim.
OL,16,FHe collapsed and died minutes later,
OL,17,Fshortly before midnight.
OL,19,FThe knife scabbard was left at the
OL,20,Fscene and was found to have the
OL,21,Fdefendant's DNA on it.
