OL,4,Cold Harry Pitman on New Year's Eve
OL,6,FAfter a media appeal, Lloyd-Hall went
OL,7,Fto Hammersmith police station with his
OL,8,Ffather on January 4 2024.
OL,10,FAt his trials, college student Lloyd-
OL,11,FHall, who was 16 at the time, claimed
OL,12,Fhe thought he had only hit Harry with
OL,13,Fthe sheath in an attempt to get Harry
OL,14,Faway from him.
