OL,6,FHe said he ran off not realising what
OL,7,Fhad happened because he was holding a
OL,8,Fknife and knew there were police
OL,9,Fofficers nearby.
OL,11,FJurors were told Lloyd-Hall had
OL,12,Fattention deficit hyperactivity
OL,13,Fdisorder (ADHD) and was suffering from
OL,14,Fcannabis-induced paranoia.
OL,16,FIn mitigation, defence barrister David
OL,17,FBentley KC referred to a handwritten
OL,18,Fletter in Lloyd-Hall had said: "I'm
OL,19,Fsorry for causing this, honestly I am."
