OL,6,FMr Bentley said: "He is not going to
OL,7,Fsay it is not his fault. He now
OL,8,Frealises that at 16 he was a naive,
OL,9,Fimmature, stubborn teenager who should
OL,10,Fhave been seeking help for his
OL,11,Fproblems.
OL,13,F"He also recognises he has not only
OL,14,Fcaused terrible trauma to Harry's
OL,15,Ffamily but also his family."
